Do you think it's changed how you think about like because I think Stack Overflow is all

00:20:49.199 --> 00:20:51.719
like Creative Commons license.

00:20:51.719 --> 00:20:56.800
So like kind of legally, all the LLMs are, you know, providers are fine.

